THE SCOW 39 E. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. February 4, 1903.) No. 55. Appeal from the District Court of the United States-for the Southern District of New York. Peter S. Carter, for appellants. Samuel A. Park, for appellees.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Decree of District Court affirmed, with interest and costs.
